==English==
===Noun===
'''octopi'''

# a plural form of [[octopus]].

===Etymology===
* The ''-i'' plural comes from the belief that ''[[octopus]]'' is a [[Wiktionary Appendix:Latin second declension|Latin second declension]] noun. In fact, it belongs to the [[Wiktionary Appendix:Greek third declension|Greek third declension]]. The usual plural is ''[[octopuses]]''; ''[[octopodes]]'' is the Greek plural, which is also correct.